@startuml C1_Manage_Resources_Scenario_View
title C1 – Manage Resources (Cenário de Uso)

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
rectangle "PLMS (Port Logistics Management System)" as PLMS

Officer --> PLMS : Solicita listar/gerir Resources via UI
PLMS --> Officer : Mostra lista / formulário de edição

PLMS --> "External IAM Provider (OAuth 2.0)" : Delegates authentication
PLMS --> "PLMS Database" : Persiste Resources

note right of PLMS
 Cenário típico: o Oficial entra no UI, autentica-se e cria/edita
 resources (cranes, trucks, etc.) que ficam persistidos na base de dados.
end note

@enduml